responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "22ED17AA4ECC06DEDE1E7CAE4322C91B", "Greed of course. Everyone can fall victim to this. Even I. My soul is ravenous for the lost lore of the Highwayman Hills. A lore so aged that is predates the Thana\'Dell name it once bore. I seek an age before ages. Alas, such an expedition is far too dangerous for a scholar, an akhunda.")
name: MADD_0005B_OSG_AkhundaWazoo_9
